{"tid":1257704,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗返巴塞求重生　屁馬咁都肯制？","createTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:20:24.000Z","uid":268711,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb3c5bf222e7f8b4197da57f7b249d9e5d86a54","tid":1257704,"uid":268711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"今季喺法甲巴黎聖日耳門(PSG)愈踢愈冇癮嘅巴西球星尼馬，一直有傳佢想重返巴塞隆拿，尋求重生，根據今日《每日體育報》報道，原來尼馬已經同巴塞傾掂晒個人條件，<span style=\"color: red;\">大幅減薪之餘，就連之前喺法庭告緊巴塞話要追收嘅忠誠獎金都要放棄，兼夾公開道歉</span>。雖然話條件勁辣，不過話尼馬都照樣應承，依家只要巴塞同PSG傾掂埋轉會費，就可以成事。 <br />\n<br />\n《每日體育報》話巴塞已經同尼馬達成口頭協議，雙方將會簽約5年，而<span style=\"color: red;\">尼馬年薪會減一半，即係由原本喺PSG嘅除稅後年薪3,600萬歐元，變成新約嘅1,800萬歐元</span>。至於之前尼馬離開巴塞嗰陣，因為巴塞唔肯找佢筆2,600萬歐元嘅續約<span style=\"color: red;\">忠誠</span>獎金，呢位巴西球星將要撤控放棄唔收錢。仲有，據聞尼馬為向巴塞表示<span style=\"color: red;\">忠誠</span>，佢將願意為兩年前離隊作公開道歉，兼承認當日過檔PSG係個錯誤，佢希望用呢個舉動可以得到巴塞會方及球迷諒解。 <br />\n<br />\n點都好，依家仲要睇巴塞傾唔傾得掂PSG放人。查實之前PSG曾經打算用尼馬向曼聯換保羅普巴，但就已經畀「紅魔鬼」拒絕。至於<span style=\"color: red;\">巴塞就打算向PSG開出一億歐元加菲臘比古天奴作交換</span>，睇落都算係唔差嘅價位，PSG有得諗喎！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLzbzuG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLzbzuG.gif&h=4c89267a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fd358bae5953d62039ae48415b052f20049aef2","tid":1257704,"uid":35842,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJn1ce0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJn1ce0.png&h=0aeb1555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/seekforg20help\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fseekforg20help&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=fb6f9b2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/seekforg20help</a><br />\n由於聽日步行路線比較複雜，所以我地會用呢個頻道keep住update遊行隊伍去到咩位置，方便想中途加入既人搵到我地。所以希望大家可以幫手share呢條Channel出去，感謝！<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></div><br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3265e617f23285732ab398533829d04c1808474c","tid":1257704,"uid":151933,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:48:01.000Z","msg":"美斯 so9都唔細 過兩三年就會走<br />\n到時尼馬唔止呢個價<br />\n同埋佢地走咗可以攞正牌做大佬 到時人工一定高"},{"pid":"de1717e8d531db08c4dc84870f9a29638f8ffc64","tid":1257704,"uid":1823,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"古天奴去另一個北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a176e27531d279ce25212d8ceb532f5215df6c1","tid":1257704,"uid":34689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"古好慘"},{"pid":"0def69330ea86b2cacaa6a075165a773194b82d0","tid":1257704,"uid":3743,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4a176e27531d279ce25212d8ceb532f5215df6c1","tid":1257704,"uid":34689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"古好慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9201b2668fdc46e7ed1509545887c702d0731744","tid":1257704,"uid":5549,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"尼馬去巴黎打poker多過踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba7b18312a0bca570dba7d6ecde1c4a5320c321","tid":1257704,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0def69330ea86b2cacaa6a075165a773194b82d0","tid":1257704,"uid":3743,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4a176e27531d279ce25212d8ceb532f5215df6c1","tid":1257704,"uid":34689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"古好慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"